{"tid":1635271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【直播中】逾百人太子站悼抗爭亡靈　旺角警發射催淚彈","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:50:32.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9da854f4fca8416dab5637e2ab1dd741c073013a","tid":1635271,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"香港政府上周五（4日）宣佈引用《緊急法》強推《禁蒙面法》後，連日來的示威遍地開花。繼昨日（6日）全民佩戴口罩遊行反抗惡法後，再有網友號召民眾今日下午3時，在全港18區響應「全民V煞（V怪客）」，呼籲「香港人反抗到底！」另有網友晚間7時在旺角警署附近的港鐵太子站出口舉行「重陽悼念反送中義士追思會」，結果警署內有人淋射刺激性藍色水劑，在場市民和記者被噴中，身體不適。稍後警方在旺角警署內向彌敦道發射了至少3發子彈，當中包括催淚彈及橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/860/rnews/20191007/1644984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F860%2Frnews%2F20191007%2F1644984&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f66259e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F860%2Frnews%2F20191007%2F1644984&h=3cf7c8b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/860/rnews/20191007/1644984</a>"},{"pid":"bb47a8cb40a5f0511124c156d6c7d764fd5d4233","tid":1635271,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"}]}